metadata.description:
The Tune Crüe Backstage Pass is a priority pass that grants holders exclusive access to all IRL/Virtual Tune Crüe events,  free mint on future collections, and alpha channels for Music related topics as well as Crypto/NFTs signals. 

Holders will also have the following advantages on our upcoming launch: 

1) A discounted overall Mint price  
2) A free TuneScape NFT, a customizable “banner” style NFT  
3) The Ability to mint a second full set  during the pre-sale
metadata.name: Tune Crüe Backstage Pass
